                        <interp inst="t18380709-name-90" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>SAMUEL EVERETT</persName>
                  </hi>. I received the prisoner in charge—I had seen him in the Park a few minutes previously—I found two other handkerchiefs tied on his neck, and the prosecutor gave me another, which he claimed—one of the two was silk and the other cotton.</p>
